data.description: BACK ON THE MARKET, by no fault of the seller!   Fresh, new paint in the kitchen, January 2024.  Nestled in a peaceful, golf course neighborhood, this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom split-level home is brimming with love and potential. The 1-car attached garage provides extra storage, and the bedrooms offer ample space for a cozy retreat. The Primary Suite adds a touch of comfort with its private en-suite bathroom. The eat-in kitchen, outfitted with stainless steel appliances, flows naturally into the generous backyard, which is just waiting for your personal touch. Let's talk about that backyard! The jewel in the crown of this lovely home is the brand new covered patio, tailor-made for your outdoor enjoyment. Whether you're sipping morning coffee or hosting a casual evening get-together, this space is your ticket to leisure and privacy. Abundant natural light floods the home, creating an inviting ambiance from the moment you walk in. Don't miss the chance to experience all this home has to offer; schedule your private showing today! Inspections are welcome but being sold 'AS IS.' The SELLERS are MOTIVATED so make an offer today!
